    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid project car with strong enthusiast potential. Starts, runs, and moves under its own power, with an engine that pulls cleanly and a drivetrain that feels fundamentally intact. Not a show car and priced accordingly, but a worthwhile platform for someone who appreciates a mechanically straightforward driver needing cosmetic and TLC items. Good candidate for a budget build, parts runner, or weekend revival. Selling as-is.",
