      "description": "Honest, rugged, and full of personality, this car is the kind of machine that still has stories left to tell. It\u2019s the perfect candidate for someone who appreciates a vehicle with character\u2014great as a budget-friendly daily, a handy spare, or a project to make your own. There\u2019s a raw charm here you just don\u2019t get from newer, polished options, and for the right buyer, it offers a practical way to get on the road without spending big. If you want something straightforward, affordable, and packed with potential, this one is worth a look.",
